# === WC2026 tool — only index.html and live_data.json should ever be pushed ===
# Strategy: ignore everything, then explicitly un-ignore the two deploy files.

# Ignore everything by default
*

# ...but always allow these
!index.html
!live_data.json
!.gitignore

# Notes:
# - The Excel DB, CSVs (squads/players/results), age_data.txt, fifa_ranks.json,
#   elo_ratings.json, and google_service_account.json stay LOCAL (never pushed).
# - Generated paste sheets (*_Fill.xlsx, Closing_Odds.xlsx), logs (*.log),
#   backups/, and the BETSiE projections .xlsx are all ignored.
# - All the .py scripts stay local too — the live tool only needs the two files above.
api_keys.json
!bracket.html
!next_match.json
